<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>Following Up — {{quoteNumber}}</title>
<style>
  body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #f4f6f9; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; color: #1a1a2e; }
  .wrapper { max-width: 600px; margin: 32px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
  .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 100%); padding: 28px 36px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
  .brand { color: #e2e8f0; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; }
  .follow-badge { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); border-radius: 6px; padding: 6px 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); font-size: 12px; }
  .body { padding: 36px; }
  .greeting { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .message { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; color: #475569; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .quote-ref { background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 8px; padding: 14px 20px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .quote-ref .label { font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.8px; }
  .quote-ref .value { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: #1e293b; }
  .items-summary { margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .item-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9; font-size: 14px; color: #334155; }
  .item-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .item-sku { font-weight: 600; }
  .footer { background: #f8fafc; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding: 20px 36px; text-align: center; color: #94a3b8; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.7; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrapper">
  <div class="header">
    <div class="brand">{{platformName}}</div>
    <div class="follow-badge">Follow-up · Day {{followUpDay}}</div>
  </div>
  <div class="body">
    <div class="greeting">Hi {{contactName}},</div>
    <p class="message">
      We're following up on the quote we sent you. We wanted to make sure you received it
      and see if you have any questions or if there's anything we can clarify.
    </p>
    <div class="quote-ref">
      <div>
        <div class="label">Quote Reference</div>
        <div class="value">{{quoteNumber}}</div>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align:right">
        <div class="label">Valid Until</div>
        <div class="value">{{validUntil}}</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="items-summary">
      <div style="font-size:12px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.8px;color:#94a3b8;margin-bottom:10px;font-weight:600;">Your Order Summary</div>
      {{#each lineItems}}
      <div class="item-row">
        <span class="item-sku">{{this.sku}}</span>
        <span>{{this.qty}} {{this.unit}}</span>
      </div>
      {{/each}}
    </div>
    <p class="message">
      If you're ready to proceed or need any changes, simply reply to this email.
      We look forward to hearing from you.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="footer">
    Quote <strong>{{quoteNumber}}</strong> · Valid until {{validUntil}}<br/>
    Generated by <strong>{{platformName}}</strong>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
